    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/5ffef1cf9435dc3b1360a79cfac12911.avif?t=1763672951\" width=613 height=66 /></span><br><br>《终极太空突击队：反击势力》是一款具有深度科幻氛围的回合制小队战术游戏。你将指挥一支被派往行星 M-8322 的特种兵战术小队，调查神秘异星生物入侵之余，还需下手铲除余孽。你的所见所闻，极有可能大幅改变历史的进程……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/e7c04fbf95afa31e8c3992a02aaa694e.poster.avif?t=1763672951\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/e7c04fbf95afa31e8c3992a02aaa694e.webm?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/e7c04fbf95afa31e8c3992a02aaa694e.mp4?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/84b6ff08f25650779da52bcdb5a2e30f.webp?t=1763672951\" width=613 height=48 /></span><br><br>带领你的太空突击队，畅玩灵感源自于UFO/XCOM和《异形》的回合制小队战术游戏。在剧情战役等多种游戏模式中，运用具有深度的技能和战斗系统。 挖掘MC83-A殖民地消亡的真相，并加入美国太空军捍卫人类！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/dfedb5c123aaf91e6095e63e06b1192f.poster.avif?t=1763672951\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/dfedb5c123aaf91e6095e63e06b1192f.webm?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/dfedb5c123aaf91e6095e63e06b1192f.mp4?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/89702fa787213780bcebc2e24c63a6d9.webp?t=1763672951\" width=613 height=29 /></span><br><br>精心配置战队，迎接各式各样的挑战！游戏内置颇具深度的小队管理系统，内含复杂的角色属性与技能选项，细致的战斗机制，当然，也少不了精心设计的物品栏。不管你是什么玩法，上百种武器和装备里总有适配的那款。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>技能系统不与职业绑定，多种被动能力自由选择<br></li><li>近战、远程武器丰富多样，后者更有各类弹药可供装填<br></li><li>黑客工具、地雷、炮塔等装置任你部署，装甲和武器留足升级空间</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/e24fbbbe17d608a0b3601d1b901ee3a5.poster.avif?t=1763672951\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/e24fbbbe17d608a0b3601d1b901ee3a5.webm?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/e24fbbbe17d608a0b3601d1b901ee3a5.mp4?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/ffb824eded7c4a4086e95a0d406c7ed3.webp?t=1763672951\" width=613 height=34 /></span><br><br>在可互动、可破坏的环境中探索与战斗。重构战场布局、建造路障、避开并利用环境危险、设置陷阱、触发链式反应、封锁气闸或者破开墙壁——不过务必小心，你能做到，敌人也不遑多让。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/6ebd25a81e039b02bf7bc75e5a975132.poster.avif?t=1763672951\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/6ebd25a81e039b02bf7bc75e5a975132.webm?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/6ebd25a81e039b02bf7bc75e5a975132.mp4?t=1763672951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1574870/extras/8ed53f72196937a513e251332250889a.webp?t=1763672951\" width=613 height=31 /></span><br><br>在各种游戏模式中将你的技能推至极限。探索多层次的难度系统，内容保证富有挑战性且引人入胜，可以说是专门为你量身打造的游戏体验。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>全面自订单人任务<br></li><li>具有独特目标的高难度多任务行动<br></li><li>在防御基地模式中建设、维护和保护你的前哨站<br></li><li>以及更多！</li></ul><br>不想自己对抗大军吗？进入多人游戏并在经典本地合作合适中对抗威胁，或使用Steam的「远程同乐」功能在在线跟其他士兵一起合作奋战。",
